# Feature Kickoff Workflow

1. Create the directory structure for the feature

   - `src/components/features/[feature-name]`
   - `src/app/api/[feature-name]`
   - `tests/integration/[feature-name]`

2. Create the main component file

   - `src/components/features/[feature-name]/[feature-name]-main.tsx`

3. Create a Storybook story

   - `src/components/features/[feature-name]/[feature-name].stories.tsx`

4. Create an API route handler (if needed)

   - `src/app/api/[feature-name]/route.ts`

5. Create an integration test file
   - `tests/integration/[feature-name]/[feature-name].test.ts`
